"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-11-Chinese-golfer-Lin-Xiyu-happy-after-earning-bronze-medal-at-Paris-2024-1vYCYbj7blC-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Lin Xiyu of China earned the women's golf bronze medal at the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics, by battling back to claim third place in the final round on Saturday.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Xiyu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Xiyu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Xiyu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Xiyu\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.997342774940327, \"rank\": 0.0022772705889185763, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After becoming the second Chinese golfer to clinch an Olympic medal following Feng Shanshan at Rio 2016, Lin said she was satisfied with her performance in Paris.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.6428115712065408, \"rank\": 0.5083897690983166, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan_Feng\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Feng Shanshan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan_Feng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan_Feng\"}, {\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999993022716058, \"rank\": 6.977288569903371e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel quite amazing.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know I had a chance today, but I know it's going to be a very tough battle,\\\" Lin told CGTN Sports Scene's Jiang Mengxi.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.38496908821173e-22, \"text\": \"CGTN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I did not have the best start I am asking for.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am very proud of myself the way I fought back at the end.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's good enough to win a medal and that's even better.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am very overwhelming right now.\\\"\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin climbed four places over the last 18 holes and said her secret was staying consistent despite a slow start.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was a little disappointed when I see so far back,\\\" Lin said.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But then I said to myself, I have been playing very consistent this week and I think at the back nine, the consistency is going to be a very good weapon.\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I just need to keep doing what I have been doing.\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And, and also I stopped looking at the scoreboard.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just wanted to play my own golf.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have a good game plan, and then I executed it really well and then it ended up good enough to give me a medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also revealed that she learned a lot from Feng and said the two had a memorable conversation before Lin departed for Paris.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1614, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999993022716058, \"rank\": 6.977288569903371e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I get to talk to Shanshan right before I leave for Paris,\\\" Lin said.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1640, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan\", \"score\": 0.9992143901078622, \"rank\": 0.0007862275603778881, \"text\": \"Shanshan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan\"}, {\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999993022716058, \"rank\": 6.977288569903371e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was explaining my anxiety and I was like, 'I do not know what to what to expect here.'\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then she just asked me one question: if this is your third Olympic or your last Olympics, what kind of finish you think you will be satisfied with yourself.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I thought about it and I said, 'well, medal, of course.'\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then she said, well, then that's the goal.\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have nothing to lose.\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have to keep grinding out.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing's going to be in the way when I am fully focused on this target and then I think that was a really important conversation.\\\"\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": []}]}"